<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/103000379/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """During the progressive evaluation period:
The final grade will be calculated using a weighted average as above.
Discussions are non-recoverable.

For the global evaluation:
The assignment will have to be re-submitted.
Those quizzes that have not been performed will have to be performed.
The score for the discussion part will be taken from the progressive evaluation period.

For the extraordinary evaluation, students will have to perform an exam. After 2 submission trials (during progressive evaluation and global evaluation), if a student has not been able to pass the course, it means that the assignments mode is not suitable for him/her. Therefore, a different evaluation method should be used. In any case, the score for the discussion part will be taken from the progressive evaluation period."""@es ;
    ns1:hasEvaluationTrial <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/103000379/2025-26/evaluation/trial1>,
